==English==
=== Noun ===
'''bampot'''
# (''Scottish English slang'') [[idiot]]; an objectionable and foolish person

Can also be used as a slang name for a small type of fish which can be caught with a 'bampotbox' - a small blue tupperware tub. 

This term is often used affectionately among close friends.

